  <brief_title>Optimal Dose of Propofol for Induction of Deep Sedation for Brain MRI Scanning in Children With Cerebral Palsy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Optimal Dose of Propofol for Induction of Deep Sedation for Brain MRI Scanning in Children With Cerebral Palsy</official_title>
